Privacy Policy for Parall

Effective Date: [ Aug 5 2025]

Parall ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how third-party services integrated into our app may collect and use data. Parall itself does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable user information.
1. Information We Do Not Collect

We do not:

    Collect or store personal data such as name, email address, phone number, or location.

    Track user behavior or app usage for profiling.

    Share any user information with external parties.

2. Third-Party Services and Data Collection

Parall uses the following third-party libraries and services that may collect certain information automatically, such as:

    Device type, operating system, and model

    IP address

    App performance and crash data

    Advertising ID and interaction data (if ads are shown)

| Library / Service                                        | Purpose                      | Privacy Policy Link                                                                                     |
| -------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Google Play Services**                                 | Core Android functionality   | [Google Play Services Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)                              |
| **Google AdMob / Google Ads**                            | Advertising                  | [Google Advertising Privacy & Terms](https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads)                      |
| **Firebase Crashlytics**                                 | Crash reporting              | [Firebase Crashlytics Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)                      |
| **Firebase Analytics**                                   | App usage analytics          | [Firebase Analytics Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics)                     |
| **Firebase (General)**                                   | Backend services             | [Firebase Privacy and Security](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)                            |
| **Glide**                                                | Image loading                | [Glide GitHub](https://github.com/bumptech/glide) *(Glide does not collect personal data by default)*   |
| **OkHttp**                                               | Network communication        | [OkHttp GitHub](https://square.github.io/okhttp/) *(Library itself doesn‚Äôt collect data)*               |
| **nanohttpd**                                            | Lightweight HTTP server      | [nanohttpd GitHub](https://github.com/NanoHttpd/nanohttpd)                                              |
| **Google Play Services Nearby API**                      | Nearby device communication  | [Nearby Privacy Policy](https://developers.google.com/nearby/overview)                                  |
| **AndroidX Core / Flexbox / SplashScreen / Xor Library** | UI and performance libraries | [AndroidX Libraries](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx) *(Do not collect data themselves)* |

