4. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Parall is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children. However, some third-party services used may collect data in accordance with their own terms.
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

